<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title><%= content_for?(:title) ? yield(:title).force_encoding('utf-8') + " :FOFA网站信息库": "FOFA -- 最全最准确的网站库 -- fofa.so" %></title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>
    <%= render 'layouts/navbar' %>

  <div class="container">
    <% flash.each do |key,value| %>
        <div class="page-header alert <%if key.to_s=='alert' %>alert-warning<%else%>alert-success<%end%> alert-dismissible ade in" role="alert">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            <span class="sr-only">关闭</span></button>
          <strong>提示：</strong> <%=value%>
        </div>
    <% end %>

    <%= yield %>

    <footer >
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">

          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><%= link_to "提交网站", "/userhost/index"  %></li>
            <li class="pull-right"><a href="#top">回到顶部</a></li>
            <li><a href="/info/about">技术说明</a></li>
            </li>
            <li><%= link_to "联系我们", "/info/contact" %></li>
          </ul>
          
          <p>本网站基于Rails，<a href="http://getbootstrap.com" rel="nofollow">Bootstrap</a>等构架。推荐使用Chrome和Firefox、Saferi等浏览器浏览。</p>
          <p>通过邮箱联系站长 <a href="mailto:root@fofa.so">root@fofa.so</a>.</p>
            
        <p><% if @show_ws_link%><script type="text/javascript" src="http://links.webscan.360.cn"></script><%end%></p>


        </div>
      </div>

    </footer>


  </div>


  <script>
      (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
          (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
              m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
      })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');

      ga('create', 'UA-45987479-1', 'fofa.so');
      ga('send', 'pageview');

  </script>
</body>
</html>
